          <para id="id1167453292927">SIMPLICITY - see a need, identify a problem, think ‘What if?’ and become an inventor. Think of a nappy pin - you know, to hold the baby’s nappy firmly on. Did your mom use them for you? Or are you a modern baby who only wore disposable nappies? How are these modern nappies kept on the baby? I’m sure modern moms are thrilled to bits about the new invention. (Probably baby too – who wants to be pricked in the tummy with a nappy pin!!)</para>
          <para id="id4561703">I am sure that you have all wished someone would invent a HOMEWORK ROBOT.</para>
          <para id="id1167457516832">HERE IS THE CHALLENGE</para>
          <para id="id1167453293972">Invent a wacky invention of your own.</para>
          <list id="id1167453414445" list-type="bulleted">
            <item>What NEED/PROBLEM will it address?</item>
            <item>How will it make life easier and for whom?</item>
            <item>Explain how it works.</item>
            <item>Draw it.</item>
            <item>Design a label for your invention.</item>
            <item>Name it.</item>
          </list>
          <table id="id1167461639158" summary="">
