          </table>
          <para id="id1167457615191">Wow! I am sure you are a whole lot more <emphasis effect="bold">clued up</emphasis> about inventions and inventors now. So, just to end off, let us take a look at these clues and see if you can match them with the invention. Should be a piece of cake for you now!!</para>
